data.description: MAJOR MAKE-OVER!! This beautiful home in the desirable, gated neighborhood of Summerglen looks and feels like new! Brand new hardwood flooring, fresh paint throughtout the entire home and kitchen updates. The home sits on a large, greenbelt lot and boasts an open floor plan, lots of natural light and large bedrooms. The backyard is large and perfect for a pool with a half bathroom right off the back of the house. Located in the exemplary Northeast ISD - elementary school right outside gate. NO CITY TAX!
